data.description: INCREDIBLE Opportunity to own an ORIGINAL OWNER Brick Front RANCH Home located in the quiet community of Chandler Plantation! SPECTACULAR Curb Appeal featuring Oversized 3/4+ acre Lot with Private Backyard room to garden, Outdoor covered Patio with New ceiling fan, and Spacious Side Yard providing a large level play area for the kids and room for all to enjoy the beautiful outdoors! SPACIOUS Owner's Suite with large walk in closet and Spa-like Bath including double vanities, separate walk in shower and whirlpool tub. There are 2 additional secondary bedrooms with full bath via hallway access - One of the secondary bedrooms doubles as a Home Office with French doors catering to today's work from home lifestyle. Vaulted Great Room with Fireplace and Gas Logs. Separate Dining Room with enhanced moldings as well as a breakfast room off of the kitchen. Laundry Room is off garage with utility sink. Oversized side entry garage provides ample space for your vehicles including a SEPARATE FINISHED ROOM off garage which is PERFECT for all of your storage needs! Within walking distance to Cooper Elementary and McConnell Middle and part of the Archer HS District. Optional HOA. Great opportunity for an Empty Nester or First time home buyers to get in and add their finishing touches! 2022 ROOF and 2022 Furnace. Welcome Home to 2978 Mary Alice Trail!
